node.text:
@hoodrichantuan Happy birthday best friend !
Life has been rough on you, and I’m glad I could be there for you and to these days ,I’m glad I can call you anytime and you’ll listen .Universe made sure to put me through really dark times but it also made sure to sent you whenever I was broken and hopeless. You’re one of the most genuine and humble people I’ve ever met and losing you would be embarrassing. You saw me at my worst ,the lowest and never left but keep being loyal friend. Today is your day ,I want to make sure that I’ll be by your side whenever you need help ,to share happy moments or dark times in your life . Life knows exactly what to do and it sent you at the right time and we saved each other. Forever thankful to you
